    linear and nonlinear damping, various cross terms, additional mixed nonlinearities,
    and includes a possible parametric time-dependent forcing term (e.g., sinusoidal forcing).

    Variables:
    - x0: time t (optional linear time dependence)
    - x1: position at time t
    - x2: velocity at time t

    Parameters:
    - params (np.ndarray): Trainable coefficients used by the equation skeleton.
