    - Damping terms linear and quadratic in velocity
    - Cross terms between position and velocity up to cubic order
    - Clear separation of time-dependent drift terms at the end

    Parameters:
        x0 (np.ndarray): time array
        x1 (np.ndarray): position array at time t
        x2 (np.ndarray): velocity array at time t
        params (np.ndarray): array of 12 parameters [p0,...p11]

            p0 : constant offset
