    Parameters:
    - x0 (np.ndarray): time variable
    - x1 (np.ndarray): position at time t
    - x2 (np.ndarray): velocity at time t
    - params (np.ndarray): array of parameters with length >= 12

    Parameter interpretation:
        params[0]: constant offset (external forcing or bias)
        params[1]: linear coefficient for time (x0)
        params[8]: quadratic coefficient for time (x0^2)
