    Model form inspired by nonlinear oscillator physics with extended nonlinearities:

        y = c0 
          + c1 * t 
          + c2 * x 
          + c3 * v 
          + c4 * x^3 
          + c5 * v^3 
          + c6 * v*x^2 
          + c7 * v^2*x
          + c8 * t*x
          + c9 * t*v
          + c10 * x^2
          + c11 * v^2

        plus additional mixed terms involving time*position² and position*velocity*time interactions.
